summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending Plat 34E, page 99 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone the southern 30 feet of Lot 14, also known as 626 - 4th Avenue West, from Lowrise 3 (L3) to Midrise (MR) and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Chris and James C.Y. Koh C.F. 298557).
